=09=09<h3><A style=3D"color: #003366;text-decoration: underline;" HREF=3D=
"http://www=2Encpa=2Eorg/sub/dpd/index=2Ephp?Article_ID=3D22654&utm_sou=
rce=3Dnewsletter&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3DDPD">Health Care Law=
's Insurance Tax Will Raise Premium Costs</a></h3>
=09=09<p style=3D"margin-bottom: 1em; font-size:13px;">On average, the =
cost of a family health insurance plan sold through a large employer co=
uld cost about $7,200 more over 10 years -- about $720 per year -- unde=
r President Obama's health care law=2E=2E=2E</p>
=09=09<p style=3D"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;color: #666;font-size: =
11px;margin: 0 0 12px;padding-bottom: 4px;text-align: right;">THE HILL/=
AMERICA'S HEALTH INSURANCE PLANS</p>
=09=09
=09=09<!--<p style=3D"color: #000033;font-size: 11px;margin:0;padding:0=
