"http://www=2Encpa=2Eorg/sub/dpd/index=2Ephp?Article_ID=3D22655&utm_sou=
rce=3Dnewsletter&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3DDPD">States Should J=
ust Say No to Medicaid Expansion</a></h3>
=09=09<p style=3D"margin-bottom: 1em; font-size:13px;">The number of Te=
xas doctors willing to accept new Medicaid patients has declined from 4=
2 percent in 2010 to 31 percent in 2012=2E=2E=2E</p>
